headline.print_headline: Retired U.S. Navy Commander Pleads Guilty in Bribery Scandal
headline.main: Retired U.S. Navy Commander Pleads Guilty in Bribery Scandal

lead_paragraph: A retired U.S. Navy commander pleaded guilty to federal conspiracy charges on Thursday in connection with a wide-ranging corruption investigation of a Singapore-based defense contractor.
